## 4. Data Storage and Security
Div-E does not transmit or store any personal data on external servers.  
Any information collected by Google AdMob is handled securely under Google‚Äôs data protection and compliance frameworks (GDPR, CCPA, etc.).

---

## 5. Your Choices
You can limit or disable personalized advertising on your device:

- **iOS:** *Settings ‚Üí Privacy & Security ‚Üí Tracking* ‚Üí toggle off ‚ÄúAllow Apps to Request to Track.‚Äù  
- **Apple Advertising:** *Settings ‚Üí Privacy & Security ‚Üí Apple Advertising* ‚Üí toggle off ‚ÄúPersonalized Ads.‚Äù  
- You may also reset your Advertising Identifier at any time.

